quran[169]{c,v,t}:
  33,31,WE MEN JEKNUT MINKUNNE LILLAHI WE RESULIHI WE TA’MEL SALIHÆN NU’UTIHA ‘EXHREHA MERRETEJNI WE ‘A’TEDNA LEHA RIZKÆN KERIMÆN
  33,32,JA NISA’E EN-NEBIJI LESTUNNE KE’EHEDIN MINE EN-NISA’ ‘INI ETTEKAJTUNNE FELA TEHDA’NE BIL-KAWLI FEJETME’AL-LEDHI FI KALBIHI MEREDUN WE KULNE KAWLÆN MA’RUFÆN
  33,33,WE KARNE FI BUJUTIKUNNE WE LA TEBERREXHNE TEBERRUXHEL-XHAHILIJETIL-’ULA WE ‘EKIMNE ES-SELÆTE WE ‘ATINE EZ-ZEKÆTE WE ‘ETI’NEL-LAHE WE RESULEHU ‘INNEMA JURIDU ELLAHU LIJUDH/HIBE ‘ANKUMU ER-RIXHSE ‘EHLEL-BEJTI WE JUTEHHIREKUM TETHIRÆN
  33,34,WE EDHKURNE MA JUTLA FI BUJUTIKUNNE MIN ‘AJATI ELLAHI WEL-HIKMETI ‘INNALL-LLAHE KANE LETIFÆN HABIRÆN
  33,35,‘INNEL-MUSLIMINE WEL-MUSLIMATI WEL-MU’UMININE WEL-MU’UMINATI WEL-KANITINE WEL-KANITATI WE ES-SADIKINE WE ES-SADIKATI WE ES-SABIRINE WE ES-SABIRATI WEL-HASHI’INE WEL-HASHI’ATI WEL-MUTESEDDIKINE WEL-MUTESEDDIKATI WE ES-SA’IMINE WE ES-SA’IMATI WEL-HAFIDHINE
  33,36,WE MA KANE LIMU’UMININ WE LA MU’UMINETIN ‘IDHA KADALLAHU WE RESULUHU ‘EMRÆN ‘EN JEKUNE LEHUMUL-HIJERETU MIN ‘EMRIHIM WE MEN JA’SI ELLAHE WE RESULEHU FEKAD DELLE DELALÆN MUBINÆN
  33,37,WE ‘IDH TEKULU LILLEDHI ‘EN’AMEL-LAHU ‘ALEJHI WE ‘EN’AMTE ‘ALEJHI ‘EMSIK ‘ALEJKE ZEWXHEKE WE ETTEKI ELLAHE WE TUHFI FI NEFSIKE MALLAHU MUBDIHI WE TEHSHA EN-NASE WEL-LAHU ‘EHEKKU ‘EN TEHSHAHU FELEMMA KADA ZEJDUN MINHA WETERÆN ZEWWEXHNAKEHA LIKEJ LA JEKUNE
  33,38,MA KANE ‘ALA EN-NEBIJI MIN HEREXHIN FIMA FEREDEL-LAHU LEHU SUNNETEL-LAHI FIL-LEDHINE HALEW MIN KABLU WE KANE ‘EMRU ELLAHI KADERÆN MEKDURÆN
  33,39,EL-LEDHINE JUBELLIGUNE RISALATI ELLAHI WE JEHSHEWNEHU WE LA JEHSHEWNE ‘EHEDÆN ‘ILLALLAHE WE KEFA BILLAHI HESIBÆN
  33,40,MA KANE MUHEMMEDUN ‘EBA ‘EHEDIN MIN RIXHALIKUM WE LEKIN RESULEL-LAHI WE HATEME EN-NEBIJINE WE KANEL-LAHU BIKULLI SHEJ’IN ‘ALIMÆN
  33,41,JA ‘EJJUHAL-LEDHINE ‘AMENU EDHKURU ELLAHE DHIKRÆN KETHIRÆN
  33,42,WE SEBBIHUHU BUKRETEN WE ‘ESILÆN
  33,43,HUWEL-LEDHI JUSELLI ‘ALEJKUM WE MELA’IKETUHU LIJUHRIXHEKUM MINE EDH-DHULUMATI ‘ILA EN-NURI WE KANE BIL-MU’UMININE REHIMÆN
  33,44,TEHIJETUHUM JEWME JELKAWNEHU SELAMUN WE ‘E’ADDE LEHUM ‘EXHRÆN KERIMÆN
  33,45,JA ‘EJJUHA EN-NEBIJU ‘INNA ‘ERSELNAKE SHAHIDÆN WE MUBESHSHIRÆN WE NEDHIRÆN
  33,46,WE DA’IÆN ‘ILA ELLAHI BI’IDHNIHI WE SIRAXHÆN MUNIRÆN
  33,47,WE BESHSHIRIL-MU’UMININE BI’ENNE LEHUM MINEL-LAHI FEDLÆN KEBIRÆN
  33,48,WE LA TUTI’IL-KAFIRINE WEL-MUNAFIKINE WE DA’ ‘EDHAHUM WE TEWEKKEL ‘ALA ELLAHI WE KEFA BILLAHI WE KILÆN
  33,49,JA ‘EJJUHAL-LEDHINE ‘AMENU ‘IDHA NEKEHTUMUL-MU’UMINATI THUMME TELLEKTUMUHUNNE MIN KABLI ‘EN TEMESSUHUNNE FEMA LEKUM ‘ALEJHINNE MIN ‘IDDETIN TA’TEDDUNEHA FEMETTI’UHUNNE WE SERRIHUHUNNE SERAHÆN XHEMILÆN
  33,50,JA ‘EJJUHA EN-NEBIJU ‘INNA ‘EHLELNA LEKE ‘EZWAXHEKEL-LATI ‘ATEJTE ‘UXHUREHUNNE WE MA MELEKET JEMINUKE MIMMA ‘EFA’EL-LAHU ‘ALEJKE WE BENATI ‘AMMIKE WE BENATI ‘AMMATIKE WE BENATI HALIKE WE BENATI HALATIKEL-LATI HAXHERNE ME’AKE WE EMRE’ETEN MU’UMINETEN ‘IN W
  33,51,TURXHI MEN TESHA’U MINHUNNE WE TU’UWI ‘ILEJKE MEN TESHA’U WE MENI EBTEGAJTE MIMMEN ‘AZELTE FELA XHUNAHE ‘ALEJKE DHALIKE ‘EDNA ‘EN TEKARRE ‘A’JUNUHUNNE WE LA JEHZENNE WE JERDEJNE BIMA ‘ATEJTEHUNNE KULLUHUNNE WEL-LAHU JA’LEMU MA FI KULUBIKUM WE KANEL-LAHU ‘
  33,52,LA JEHILLU LEKE EN-NISA’ MIN BA’DU WE LA ‘EN TEBEDDELE BIHINNE MIN ‘EZWAXHIN WE LEW ‘A’XHEBEKE HUSNUHUNNE ‘ILLA MA MELEKET JEMINUKE WE KANEL-LAHU ‘ALA KULLI SHEJ’IN REKIBÆN
  33,53,JA ‘EJJUHAL-LEDHINE ‘AMENU LA TEDHULU BUJUTE EN-NEBIJI ‘ILLA ‘EN JU’UDHENE LEKUM ‘ILA TA’AMIN GAJRE NADHIRINE ‘INAHU WE LEKIN ‘IDHA DU’ITUM FADHULU FE’IDHA TA’IMTUM FANTESHIRU WE LA MUSTE’NISINE LIHEDITHIN ‘INNE DHALIKUM KANE JU’UDHI EN-NEBIJE FEJESTEHJI
  33,54,‘IN TUBDU SHEJ’ÆN ‘EW TUHFUHU FE’INNALL-LLAHE KANE BIKULLI SHEJ’IN ‘ALIMÆN
  33,55,LA XHUNAHE ‘ALEJHINNE FI ‘ABA’IHINNE WE LA ‘EBNA’IHINNE WE LA ‘IHWANIHINNE WE LA ‘EBNA’I ‘IHWANIHINNE WE LA ‘EBNA’I ‘EHAWATIHINNE WE LA NISA’IHINNE WE LA MA MELEKET ‘EJMANUHUNNE WE ETTEKINEL-LAHE ‘INNALL-LLAHE KANE ‘ALA KULLI SHEJ’IN SHEHIDÆN
  33,56,‘INNALL-LLAHE WE MELA’IKETEHU JUSELLUNE ‘ALA EN-NEBIJI JA ‘EJJUHAL-LEDHINE ‘AMENU SELLU ‘ALEJHI WE SELLIMU TESLIMÆN
  33,57,‘INNEL-LEDHINE JU’UDHUNEL-LAHE WE RESULEHU LE’ANEHUMU ELLAHU FI ED-DUNJA WEL-’AHIRETI WE ‘E’ADDE LEHUM ‘ADHABÆN MUHINÆN
  33,58,WEL-LEDHINE JU’UDHUNEL-MU’UMININE WEL-MU’UMINATI BIGAJRI MA EKTESEBU FEKADI EHTEMELU BUHTANÆN WE ‘ITHMÆN MUBINÆN
  33,59,JA ‘EJJUHA EN-NEBIJU KUL LI’ZWAXHIKE WE BENATIKE WE NISA’IL-MU’UMININE JUDNINE ‘ALEJHINNE MIN XHELABIBIHINNE DHALIKE ‘EDNA ‘EN JU’REFNE FELA JU’UDHEJNE WE KANEL-LAHU GAFURÆN REHIMÆN
  33,60,LE’IN LEM JENTEHIL-MUNAFIKUNE WEL-LEDHINE FI KULUBIHIM MEREDUN WEL-MURXHIFUNE FIL-MEDINETI LENUGRIJENNEKE BIHIM THUMME LA JUXHAWIRUNEKE FIHA ‘ILLA KALILÆN
  33,61,MEL’UNINE ‘EJNEMA THUKIFU ‘UHIDHU WE KUTTILU TEKTILÆN
  33,62,SUNNETEL-LAHI FIL-LEDHINE HALEW MIN KABLU WE LEN TEXHIDE LISUNNETI ELLAHI TEBDILÆN
  33,63,JES’ELUKE EN-NASU ‘ANI ES-SA’ATI KUL ‘INNEMA ‘ILMUHA ‘INDEL-LAHI WE MA JUDRIKE LE’ALLE ES-SA’ATE TEKUNU KARIBÆN
  33,64,‘INNALL-LLAHE LE’ANEL-KAFIRINE WE ‘E’ADDE LEHUM SA’IRÆN
  33,65,HALIDINE FIHA ‘EBEDÆN LA JEXHIDUNE WELIJÆN WE LA NESIRÆN
  33,66,JEWME TUKALLEBU WUXHUHUHUM FI EN-NARI JEKULUNE JA LEJTENA ‘ETA’NA ELLAHE WE ‘ETA’NA ER-RESULA
  33,67,WE KALU REBBENA ‘INNA ‘ETA’NA SADETENA WE KUBERA’ENA FE’EDELLUNA ES-SEBILA
  33,68,REBBENA ‘ATIHIM DI’FEJNI MINEL-’ADHABI WEL-’ANHUM LA’NÆN KEBIRÆN
  33,69,JA ‘EJJUHAL-LEDHINE ‘AMENU LA TEKUNU KALLEDHINE ‘ADHEW MUSA FEBERRE’EHU ELLAHU MIMMA KALU WE KANE ‘INDEL-LAHI WEXHIHÆN
  33,70,JA ‘EJJUHAL-LEDHINE ‘AMENU ETTEKU ELLAHE WE KULU KAWLÆN SEDIDÆN
  33,71,JUSLIH LEKUM ‘A’MALEKUM WE JEGFIR LEKUM DHUNUBEKUM WE MEN JUTI’I ELLAHE WE RESULEHU FEKAD FAZE FEWZÆN ‘ADHIMÆN
  33,72,‘INNA ‘AREDNAL-’EMANETE ‘ALA ES-SEMAWATI WEL-’ERDI WEL-XHIBALI FE’EBEJNE ‘EN JEHMILNEHA WE ‘ESHFEKNE MINHA WE HEMELEHAL-’INSANU ‘INNEHU KANE DHELUMÆN XHEHULÆN
  33,73,LIJU’ADHDHIBEL-LAHUL-MUNAFIKINE WEL-MUNAFIKATI WEL-MUSHRIKINE WEL-MUSHRIKATI WE JETUBEL-LAHU ‘ALEL-MU’UMININE WEL-MU’UMINATI WE KANEL-LAHU GAFURÆN REHIMÆN
  34,1,EL-HEMDU LILLAHIL-LEDHI LEHU MA FI ES-SEMAWATI WE MA FIL-’ERDI WE LEHUL-HEMDU FIL-’AHIRETI WE HUWEL-HEKIMUL-HABIRU
  34,2,JA’LEMU MA JELIXHU FIL-’ERDI WE MA JEHRUXHU MINHA WE MA JENZILU MINE ES-SEMA’I WE MA JA’RUXHU FIHA WE HUWE ER-REHIMUL-GAFURU
  34,3,WE KALEL-LEDHINE KEFERU LA TE’TINA ES-SA’ATU KUL BELA WE RABBI LETE’TIJENNEKUM ‘ALIMIL-GAJBI LA JA’ZUBU ‘ANHU MITHKALU DHERRETIN FI ES-SEMAWATI WE LA FIL-’ERDI WE LA ‘ESGARU MIN DHALIKE WE LA ‘EKBERU ‘ILLA FI KITABIN MUBININ
  34,4,LIJEXHZIJEL-LEDHINE ‘AMENU WE ‘AMILU ES-SALIHATI ‘ULA’IKE LEHUM MEGFIRETUN WE RIZKUN KERIMUN
  34,5,WEL-LEDHINE SE’AW FI ‘AJATINA MU’AXHIZINE ‘ULA’IKE LEHUM ‘ADHABUN MIN RIXHZIN ‘ELIMUN
  34,6,WE JERAL-LEDHINE ‘UTUL-’ILMEL-LEDHI ‘UNZILE ‘ILEJKE MIN RABBIKE HUWEL-HEKKA WE JEHDI ‘ILA SIRATIL-’AZIZIL-HEMIDI
  34,7,WE KALEL-LEDHINE KEFERU HEL NEDULLUKUM ‘ALA REXHULIN JUNEBBI’UKUM ‘IDHA MUZZIKTUM KULLE MUMEZZEKIN ‘INNEKUM LEFI HALKIN XHEDIDIN
  34,8,‘AFTERA ‘ALA ELLAHI KEDHIBÆN ‘EM BIHI XHINNETUN BELIL-LEDHINE LA JU’UMINUNE BIL-’AHIRETI FIL-’ADHABI WE ED-DELALIL-BA’IDI
  34,9,‘EFELEM JEREW ‘ILA MA BEJNE ‘EJDIHIM WE MA HALFEHUM MINE ES-SEMA’I WEL-’ERDI ‘IN NESHE’ NEHSIF BIHIMUL-’ERDE ‘EW NUSKIT ‘ALEJHIM KISEFÆN MINE ES-SEMA’I ‘INNE FI DHALIKE LE’AJETEN LIKULLI ‘ABDIN MUNIBIN
  34,10,WE LEKAD ‘ATEJNA DAWUDE MINNA FEDLÆN JA XHIBALU ‘EWWIBI ME’AHU WET-TEJRE WE ‘ELENNA LEHUL-HEDIDE
  34,11,‘ENI A’MEL SABIGATIN WE KADDIR FI ES-SERDI WE A’MELU SALIHÆN ‘INNI BIMA TA’MELUNE BESIRUN
  34,12,WE LISULEJMANE ER-RIHE GUDUWUHA SHEHRUN WE REWAHUHA SHEHRUN WE ‘ESELNA LEHU ‘AJNEL-KITRI WE MINEL-XHINNI MEN JA’MELU BEJNE JEDEJHI BI’IDHNI RABBIHI WE MEN JEZIG MINHUM ‘AN ‘EMRINA NUDHIKHU MIN ‘ADHABI ES-SA’IRI
  34,13,JA’MELUNE LEHU MA JESHA’U MIN MEHARIBE WE TEMATHILE WE XHIFANIN KALXHEWABI WE KUDURIN RASIJATIN A’MELU ‘ALE DAWUDE SHUKRÆN WE KALILUN MIN ‘IBADIJE ESH-SHEKURU
  34,14,FELEMMA KADEJNA ‘ALEJHIL-MEWTE MA DELLEHUM ‘ALA MEWTIHI ‘ILLA DABBETUL-’ERDI TE’KULU MINSE’ETEHU FELEMMA HARRE TEBEJJENETIL-XHINNU ‘EN LEW KANU JA’LEMUNEL-GAJBE MA LEBITHU FIL-’ADHABIL-MUHINI
  34,15,LEKAD KANE LISEBE’IIN FI MESKENIHIM ‘AJETUN XHENNETANI ‘AN JEMININ WE SHIMALIN KULU MIN RIZKI RABBIKUM WE ESHKURU LEHU BELDETUN TEJJIBETUN WE REBBUN GAFURUN
  34,16,FE’A’REDU FE’ERSELNA ‘ALEJHIM SEJLEL-’ARIMI WE BEDDELNAHUM BIXHENNETEJHIM XHENNETEJNI DHEWATA ‘UKULIN HAMTIN WE ‘ETHLIN WE SHEJ’IN MIN SIDRIN KALILIN
  34,17,DHALIKE XHEZEJNAHUM BIMA KEFERU WE HEL NUXHAZI ‘ILLAL-KEFURE
  34,18,WE XHE’ALNA BEJNEHUM WE BEJNEL-KURA ELLETI BAREKNA FIHA KUREN DHAHIRETEN WE KADDERNA FIHA ES-SEJRE SIRU FIHA LEJALIJE WE ‘EJJAMÆN ‘AMININE
  34,19,FEKALU REBBENA BA’ID BEJNE ‘ESFARINA WE DHELEMU ‘ENFUSEHUM FEXHE’ALNAHUM ‘EHADITHE WE MEZZEKNAHUM KULLE MUMEZZEKIN ‘INNE FI DHALIKE LE’AJATIN LIKULLI SEBBARIN SHEKURIN
  34,20,WE LEKAD SEDDEKA ‘ALEJHIM ‘IBLISU DHENNEHU FE ETTEBA’UHU ‘ILLA FERIKÆN MINEL-MU’UMININE
  34,21,WE MA KANE LEHU ‘ALEJHIM MIN SULTANIN ‘ILLA LINA’LEME MEN JU’UMINU BIL-’AHIRETI MIMMEN HUWE MINHA FI SHEKKIN WE REBBUKE ‘ALA KULLI SHEJ’IN HEFIDHUN
  34,22,KUL ED’UL-LEDHINE ZE’AMTUM MIN DUNI ELLAHI LA JEMLIKUNE MITHKALE DHERRETIN FI ES-SEMAWATI WE LA FIL-’ERDI WE MA LEHUM FIHIMA MIN SHIRKIN WE MA LEHU MINHUM MIN DHEHIRIN
  34,23,WE LA TENFA’U ESH-SHEFA’ATU ‘INDEHU ‘ILLA LIMEN ‘EDHINE LEHU HETTA ‘IDHA FUZZI’A ‘AN KULUBIHIM KALU MADHA KALE REBBUKUM KALUL-HEKKA WE HUWEL-’ALIJUL-KEBIRU
  34,24,KUL MEN JERZUKUKUM MINE ES-SEMAWATI WEL-’ERDI KULI ELLAHU WE ‘INNA ‘EW ‘IJAKUM LE’ALA HUDEN ‘EW FI DELALIN MUBININ
  34,25,KUL LA TUS’ELUNE ‘AMMA ‘EXHREMNA WE LA NUS’ELU ‘AMMA TA’MELUNE
  34,26,KUL JEXHMA’U BEJNENA REBBUNA THUMME JEFTEHU BEJNENA BIL-HEKKI WE HUWEL-FETTAHUL-’ALIMU
  34,27,KUL ‘ERUNIJEL-LEDHINE ‘ELHEKTUM BIHI SHUREKA’E KELLA BEL HUWEL-LAHUL-’AZIZUL-HEKIMU
  34,28,WE MA ‘ERSELNAKE ‘ILLA KAFFETEN LILNNASI BESHIRÆN WE NEDHIRÆN WE LEKINNE ‘EKTHERE EN-NASI LA JA’LEMUNE
  34,29,WE JEKULUNE META HADHAL-WA’DU ‘IN KUNTUM SADIKINE
  34,30,KUL LEKUM MI’ADU JEWMIN LA TESTE’HIRUNE ‘ANHU SA’ATEN WE LA TESTEKDIMUNE
  34,31,WE KALEL-LEDHINE KEFERU LEN NU’UMINE BIHEDHAL-KUR’ANI WE LA BIEL-LEDHI BEJNE JEDEJHI WE LEW TERA ‘IDHI EDH-DHALIMUNE MEWKUFUNE ‘INDE RABBIHIM JERXHI’U BA’DUHUM ‘ILA BA’DINL-KAWLE JEKULUL-LEDHINE ESTUD’IFU LILLEDHINE ESTEKBERU LEWLA ‘ENTUM LEKUNNA MU’UMINI
  34,32,KALEL-LEDHINE ESTEKBERU LILLEDHINE ESTUD’IFU ‘ENEHNU SEDEDNAKUM ‘ANIL-HUDA BA’DE ‘IDH XHA’EKUM BEL KUNTUM MUXHRIMINE
  34,33,WE KALEL-LEDHINE ESTUD’IFU LILLEDHINE ESTEKBERU BEL MEKRUL-LEJLI WE EN-NEHARI ‘IDH TE’MURUNENA ‘EN NEKFURE BILLAHI WE NEXH’ALE LEHU ‘ENDADÆN WE ‘ESERRU EN-NEDAMETE LEMMA RE’EWL-’ADHABE WE XHE’ALNAL-’EGLALE FI ‘A’NAKIL-LEDHINE KEFERU HEL JUXHZEWNE ‘ILLA MA
  34,34,WE MA ‘ERSELNA FI KARJETIN MIN NEDHIRIN ‘ILLA KALE MUTREFUHA ‘INNA BIMA ‘URSILTUM BIHI KAFIRUNE
  34,35,WE KALU NEHNU ‘EKTHERU ‘EMWALÆN WE ‘EWLADÆN WE MA NEHNU BIMU’ADHDHEBINE
  34,36,KUL ‘INNE RABBI JEBSUTU ER-RIZKA LIMEN JESHA’U WE JEKDIRU WE LEKINNE ‘EKTHERE EN-NASI LA JA’LEMUNE
  34,37,WE MA ‘EMWALUKUM WE LA ‘EWLADUKUM BI-ETI TUKARRIBUKUM ‘INDENA ZULFA ‘ILLA MEN ‘AMENE WE ‘AMILE SALIHÆN FE’ULA’IKE LEHUM XHEZA’U ED-DI’FI BIMA ‘AMILU WE HUM FIL-GURUFATI ‘AMINUNE
  34,38,WEL-LEDHINE JES’AWNE FI ‘AJATINA MU’AXHIZINE ‘ULA’IKE FIL-’ADHABI MUHDERUNE
  34,39,KUL ‘INNE RABBI JEBSUTU ER-RIZKA LIMEN JESHA’U MIN ‘IBADIHI WE JEKDIRU LEHU WE MA ‘ENFEKTUM MIN SHEJ’IN FEHUWE JUHLIFUHU WE HUWE HAJRU ER-RAZIKINE
  34,40,WE JEWME JEHSHURUHUM XHEMI’ÆN THUMME JEKULU LILMELA’IKETI ‘EHA’UULA’ ‘IJAKUM KANU JA’BUDUNE
  34,41,KALU SUBHANEKE ‘ENTE WELIJUNA MIN DUNIHIM BEL KANU JA’BUDUNEL-XHINNE ‘EKTHERUHUM BIHIM MU’UMINUNE
  34,42,FALJEWME LA JEMLIKU BA’DUKUM LIBA’DIN NEF’ÆN WE LA DERRÆN WE NEKULU LILLEDHINE DHELEMU DHUKU ‘ADHABE EN-NARI ELLETI KUNTUM BIHA TUKEDHDHIBUN
  34,43,WE ‘IDHA TUTLA ‘ALEJHIM ‘AJATUNA BEJJINATIN KALU MA HADHA ‘ILLA REXHULUN JURIDU ‘EN JESUDDEKUM ‘AMMA KANE JA’BUDU ‘ABA’UUKUM WE KALU MA HADHA ‘ILLA ‘IFKUN MUFTEREN WE KALEL-LEDHINE KEFERU LILHEKKI LEMMA XHA’EHUM ‘IN HADHA ‘ILLA SIHRUN MUBINUN
  34,44,WE MA ‘ATEJNAHUM MIN KUTUBIN JEDRUSUNEHA WE MA ‘ERSELNA ‘ILEJHIM KABLEKE MIN NEDHIRIN
  34,45,WE KEDHDHEBEL-LEDHINE MIN KABLIHIM WE MA BELEGU MI’SHARE MA ‘ATEJNAHUM FEKEDHDHEBU RUSULI FEKEJFE KANE NEKIRI
  34,46,KUL ‘INNEMA ‘A’IDHUKUM BIWAHIDETIN ‘EN TEKUMU LILLAHI METHNA WE FURADA THUMME TETEFEKKERU MA BISAHIBIKUM MIN XHINNETIN ‘IN HUWE ‘ILLA NEDHIRUN LEKUM BEJNE JEDEJ ‘ADHABIN SHEDIDIN
  34,47,KUL MA SE’ELTUKUM MIN ‘EXHRIN FEHUWE LEKUM ‘IN ‘EXHRIJE ‘ILLA ‘ALA ELLAHI WE HUWE ‘ALA KULLI SHEJ’IN SHEHIDUN
  34,48,KUL ‘INNE RABBI JEKDHIFU BIL-HEKKI ‘ALLAMUL-GUJUBI
  34,49,KUL XHA’EL-HEKKU WE MA JUBDI’UL-BATILU WE MA JU’IDU
  34,50,KUL ‘IN DELELTU FE’INNEMA ‘EDILLU ‘ALA NEFSI WE ‘INI EHTEDEJTU FEBIMA JUHI ‘ILEJJE RABBI ‘INNEHU SEMI’UN KARIBUN
  34,51,WE LEW TERA ‘IDH FEZI’U FELA FEWTE WE ‘UHIDHU MIN MEKANIN KARIBIN
  34,52,WE KALU ‘AMENNA BIHI WE ‘ENNA LEHUMUT-TENAWUSHU MIN MEKANIN BA’IDIN
  34,53,WE KAD KEFERU BIHI MIN KABLU WE JEKDHIFUNE BIL-GAJBI MIN MEKANIN BA’IDIN
  34,54,WE HILE BEJNEHUM WE BEJNE MA JESHTEHUNE KEMA FU’ILE BI’ESHJA’IHIM MIN KABLU ‘INNEHUM KANU FI SHEKKIN MURIBIN
  35,1,EL-HEMDU LILLAHI FATIRI ES-SEMAWATI WEL-’ERDI XHA’ILIL-MELA’IKETI RUSULÆN ‘ULI ‘EXHNIHETIN METHNA WE THULATHE WE RUBA’A JEZIDU FIL-HALKI MA JESHA’U ‘INNALL-LLAHE ‘ALA KULLI SHEJ’IN KADIRUN
  35,2,MA JEFTEHI ELLAHU LILNNASI MIN REHMETIN FELA MUMSIKE LEHA WE MA JUMSIK FELA MURSILE LEHU MIN BA’DIHI WE HUWEL-’AZIZUL-HEKIMU
  35,3,JA ‘EJJUHA EN-NASU EDHKURU NI’METEL-LAHI ‘ALEJKUM HEL MIN HALIKIN GAJRU ELLAHI JERZUKUKUM MINE ES-SEMA’I WEL-’ERDI LA ‘ILAHE ‘ILLA HUWE FE’ENNA TU’UFEKUNE
  35,4,WE ‘IN JUKEDHDHIBUKE FEKAD KUDHDHIBET RUSULUN MIN KABLIKE WE ‘ILA ELLAHI TURXHA’UL-’UMURU
  35,5,JA ‘EJJUHA EN-NASU ‘INNE WA’DEL-LAHI HEKKUN FELA TEGURRENNEKUMUL-HEJA ETU ED-DUNJA WE LA JEGURRENNEKUM BILLAHIL-GARURU
  35,6,‘INNE ESH-SHEJTANE LEKUM ‘ADUWUN FE ETTEHIDHUHU ‘ADUWÆN ‘INNEMA JED’U HIZBEHU LIJEKUNU MIN ‘ESHABI ES-SA’IRI
  35,7,EL-LEDHINE KEFERU LEHUM ‘ADHABUN SHEDIDUN WEL-LEDHINE ‘AMENU WE ‘AMILU ES-SALIHATI LEHUM MEGFIRETUN WE ‘EXHRUN KEBIRUN
  35,8,‘EFEMEN ZUJJINE LEHU SU’U ‘AMELIHI FERE’AHU HESENÆN FE’INNALL-LLAHE JUDILLU MEN JESHA’U WE JEHDI MEN JESHA’U FELA TEDH/HEB NEFSUKE ‘ALEJHIM HESERATIN ‘INNALL-LLAHE ‘ALIMUN BIMA JESNA’UNE
  35,9,WEL-LAHUL-LEDHI ‘ERSELE ER-RIJAHE FETUTHIRU SEHABÆN FESUKNAHU ‘ILA BELEDIN MEJJITIN FE’EHJEJNA BIHIL-’ERDE BA’DE MEWTIHA KEDHALIKE EN-NUSHURU
  35,10,MEN KANE JURIDUL-’IZZETE FELILLAHIL-’IZZETU XHEMI’ÆN ‘ILEJHI JES’ADUL-KELIMUT-TEJJIBU WEL-’AMELU ES-SALIHU JERFA’UHU WEL-LEDHINE JEMKURUNE ES-SEJJI’ATI LEHUM ‘ADHABUN SHEDIDUN WE MEKRU ‘ULA’IKE HUWE JEBURU
  35,11,WEL-LAHU HALEKAKUM MIN TURABIN THUMME MIN NUTFETIN THUMME XHE’ALEKUM ‘EZWAXHÆN WE MA TEHMILU MIN ‘UNTHA WE LA TEDA’U ‘ILLA BI’ILMIHI WE MA JU’AMMERU MIN MU’AMMERIN WE LA JUNKASU MIN ‘UMURIHI ‘ILLA FI KITABIN ‘INNE DHALIKE ‘ALA ELLAHI JESIRUN
  35,12,WE MA JESTEWIL-BEHRANI HADHA ‘ADHBUN FURATUN SA’IGUN SHERABUHU WE HEDHA MILHUN ‘UXHAXHUN WE MIN KULLIN TE’KULUNE LEHMÆN TERIJÆN WE TESTEHRIXHUNE HILJETEN TELBESUNEHA WE TERAL-FULKE FIHI MEWAHIRE LITEBTEGU MIN FEDLIHI WE LE’ALLEKUM TESHKURUNE
  35,13,JULIXHUL-LEJLE FI EN-NEHARI WE JULIXHU EN-NEHARE FIL-LEJLI WE SEHHARE ESH-SHEMSE WEL-KAMERE KULLUN JEXHRI LI’XHELIN MUSEMMEN DHELIKUMU ELLAHU REBBUKUM LEHUL-MULKU WEL-LEDHINE TED’UNE MIN DUNIHI MA JEMLIKUNE MIN KITMIRIN
  35,14,‘IN TED’UHUM LA JESMA’U DU’A’EKUM WE LEW SEMI’U MA ESTEXHABU LEKUM WE JEWMEL-KIJAMETI JEKFURUNE BISHIRKIKUM WE LA JUNEBBI’UKE MITHLU HABIRIN
  35,15,JA ‘EJJUHA EN-NASU ‘ENTUMUL-FUKARA’U ‘ILA ELLAHI WEL-LAHU HUWEL-GANIJUL-HEMIDU
  35,16,‘IN JESHE’ JUDH/HIBKUM WE JE’TI BIHALKIN XHEDIDIN
  35,17,WE MA DHALIKE ‘ALA ELLAHI BI’AZIZIN
  35,18,WE LA TEZIRU WAZIRETUN WIZRE ‘UHRA WE ‘IN TED’U MUTHKALETUN ‘ILA HIMLIHA LA JUHMEL MINHU SHEJ’UN WE LEW KANE DHA KURBA ‘INNEMA TUNDHIRUL-LEDHINE JEHSHEWNE REBBEHUM BIL-GAJBI WE ‘EKAMU ES-SELÆTE WE MEN TEZEKKA FE’INNEMA JETEZEKKA LINEFSIHI WE ‘ILA ELLAHIL
  35,19,WE MA JESTEWIL-’A’MA WEL-BESIRU
  35,20,WE LA EDH-DHULUMATU WE LA EN-NUR
  35,21,WE LA EDH-DHILLU WE LAL-HERURU
  35,22,WE MA JESTEWIL-’EHJA’U WE LAL-’EMWATU ‘INNALL-LLAHE JUSMI’U MEN JESHA’U WE MA ‘ENTE BIMUSMI’IN MEN FIL-KUBURI
  35,23,‘IN ‘ENTE ‘ILLA NEDHIRUN
  35,24,‘INNA ‘ERSELNAKE BIL-HEKKI BESHIRÆN WE NEDHIRÆN WE ‘IN MIN ‘UMMETIN ‘ILLA HALA FIHA NEDHIRUN
  35,25,WE ‘IN JUKEDHDHIBUKE FEKAD KEDHDHEBEL-LEDHINE MIN KABLIHIM XHA’ET/HUM RUSULUHUM BIL-BEJJINATI WE BIZ-ZUBURI WE BIL-KITABIL-MUNIRI
  35,26,THUMME ‘EHADHTUL-LEDHINE KEFERU FEKEJFE KANE NEKIRI
  35,27,‘ELEM TERA ‘ENNEL-LAHE ‘ENZELE MINE ES-SEMA’I MA’EN FE’EHREXHNA BIHI THEMERATIN MUHTELIFÆN ‘ELWANUHA WE MINEL-XHIBALI XHUDEDUN BIDUN WE HUMRUN MUHTELIFUN ‘ELWANUHA WE GARABIBU SUDUN
  35,28,WE MINE EN-NASI WE ED-DEWABBI WEL-’EN’AM MUHTELIFUN ‘ELWANUHU KEDHALIKE ‘INNEMA JEHSHA ELLAHE MIN ‘IBADIHIL-’ULEMA’U ‘INNALL-LLAHE ‘AZIZUN GAFURUN
  35,29,‘INNEL-LEDHINE JETLUNE KITABEL-LAHI WE ‘EKAMU ES-SELÆTE WE ‘ENFEKU MIMMA REZEKNAHUM SIRRÆN WE ‘ALANIJETEN JERXHUNE TIXHARETEN LEN TEBURE
  35,30,LIJUWEFFIJEHUM ‘UXHUREHUM WE JEZIDEHUM MIN FEDLIHI ‘INNEHU GAFURUN SHEKURUN
  35,31,WEL-LEDHI ‘EWHEJNA ‘ILEJKE MINEL-KITABI HUWEL-HEKKU MUSEDDIKÆN LIMA BEJNE JEDEJHI ‘INNALL-LLAHE BI’IBADIHI LEHABIRUN BESIRUN
  35,32,THUMME ‘EWRETHNAL-KITABEL-LEDHINE ESTEFEJNA MIN ‘IBADINA FEMINHUM DHALIMUN LINEFSIHI WE MINHUM MUKTESIDUN WE MINHUM SABIKUN BIL-HAJRATI BI’IDHNI ELLAHI DHALIKE HUWEL-FEDLUL-KEBIRU
  35,33,XHENNATU ‘ADNIN JEDHULUNEHA JUHELLEWNE FIHA MIN ‘ESAWIRE MIN DHEHEBIN WE LU’ULU’UÆN WE LIBASUHUM FIHA HERIRUN
  35,34,WE KALUL-HEMDU LILLAHIL-LEDHI ‘EDH/HEBE ‘ANNAL-HEZENE ‘INNE REBBENA LEGAFURUN SHEKURUN
  35,35,EL-LEDHI ‘EHELLENA DAREL-MUKAMETI MIN FEDLIHI LA JEMESSUNA FIHA NESEBUN WE LA JEMESSUNA FIHA LUGUBUN
  35,36,WEL-LEDHINE KEFERU LEHUM NARU XHEHENNEME LA JUKDA ‘ALEJHIM FEJEMUTU WE LA JUHAFFEFU ‘ANHUM MIN ‘ADHABIHA KEDHALIKE NEXHZI KULLE KEFURIN
  35,37,WE HUM JESTERIHUNE FIHA REBBENA ‘EHRIXHNA NA’MEL SALIHÆN GAJREL-LEDHI KUNNA NA’MELU ‘EWELEM NU’AMMIRKUM MA JETEDHEKKERU FIHI MEN TEDHEKKERE WE XHA’EKUMU EN-NEDHIRU FEDHUKU FEMA LILDHDHALIMINE MIN NESIR
  35,38,‘INNALL-LLAHE ‘ALIMU GAJBI ES-SEMAWATI WEL-’ERDI ‘INNEHU ‘ALIMUN BIDHATI ES-SUDURI
  35,39,HUWEL-LEDHI XHE’ALEKUM HALA’IFE FIL-’ERDI FEMEN KEFERE FE’ALEJHI KUFRUHU WE LA JEZIDUL-KAFIRINE KUFRUHUM ‘INDE RABBIHIM ‘ILLA MEKTÆN WE LA JEZIDUL-KAFIRINE KUFRUHUM ‘ILLA HASARÆN
  35,40,KUL ‘ERE’EJTUM SHUREKA’EKUMUL-LEDHINE TED’UNE MIN DUNI ELLAHI ‘ERUNI MADHA HALEKU MINEL-’ERDI ‘EM LEHUM SHIRKUN FI ES-SEMAWATI ‘EM ‘ATEJNAHUM KITABÆN FEHUM ‘ALA BEJJINETIN MINHU BEL ‘IN JA’IDU EDH-DHALIMUNE BA’DUHUM BA’DÆN ‘ILLA GURURÆN
  35,41,‘INNALL-LLAHE JUMSIKU ES-SEMAWATI WEL-’ERDE ‘EN TEZULA WE LE’IN ZALETA ‘IN ‘EMSEKEHUMA MIN ‘EHEDIN MIN BA’DIHI ‘INNEHU KANE HELIMÆN GAFURÆN
  35,42,WE ‘EKSEMU BILLAHI XHEHDE ‘EJMANIHIM LE’IN XHA’EHUM NEDHIRUN LEJEKUNUNNE ‘EHDA MIN ‘IHDAL-’UMEMI FELEMMA XHA’EHUM NEDHIRUN MA ZADEHUM ‘ILLA NUFURÆN
  35,43,ESTIKBARÆN FIL-’ERDI WE MEKRE ES-SEJJI’I WE LA JEHIKUL-MEKRU ES-SEJJI’U ‘ILLA BI’EHLIHI FEHEL JENDHURUNE ‘ILLA SUNNETEL-’EWWELINE FELEN TEXHIDE LISUNNETI ELLAHI TEBDILÆN WE LEN TEXHIDE LISUNNETI ELLAHI TEHWILÆN
  35,44,‘EWELEM JESIRU FIL-’ERDI FEJENDHURU KEJFE KANE ‘AKIBETUL-LEDHINE MIN KABLIHIM WE KANU ‘ESHEDDE MINHUM KUWETEN WE MA KANEL-LAHU LIJU’XHIZEHU MIN SHEJ’IN FI ES-SEMAWATI WE LA FIL-’ERDI ‘INNEHU KANE ‘ALIMÆN KADIRÆN
  35,45,WE LEW JU’UAHIDHU ELLAHU EN-NASE BIMA KESEBU MA TEREKE ‘ALA DHEHRIHA MIN DABBETIN WE LEKIN JU’UEHHIRUHUM ‘ILA ‘EXHELIN MUSEMMEN FE’IDHA XHA’E ‘EXHELUHUM FE’INNALL-LLAHE KANE BI’IBADIHI BESIRÆN
  36,1,JA -SIN
  36,2,WEL-KUR’ANIL-HEKIMI
  36,3,‘INNEKE LEMINEL-MURSELINE
  36,4,‘ALA SIRATIN MUSTEKIMIN
  36,5,TENZILEL-’AZIZI ER-REHIMI
  36,6,LITUNDHIRE KAWMÆN MA ‘UNDHIRE ‘ABA’UUHUM FEHUM GAFILUNE
  36,7,LEKAD HEKKAL-KAWLU ‘ALA ‘EKTHERIHIM FEHUM LA JU’UMINUNE
  36,8,‘INNA XHE’ALNA FI ‘A’NAKIHIM ‘EGLALÆN FEHIJE ‘ILAL-’EDHKANI FEHUM MUKMEHUNE
  36,9,WE XHE’ALNA MIN BEJNI ‘EJDIHIM SEDDÆN WE MIN HALFIHIM SEDDÆN FE’EGSHEJNAHUM FEHUM LA JUBSIRUNE
  36,10,WE SEWA’UN ‘ALEJHIM ‘E’ENDHERTEHUM ‘EM LEM TUNDHIRHUM LA JU’UMINUNE
  36,11,‘INNEMA TUNDHIRU MENI ETTEBE’A EDH-DHIKRE WE HASHIJE ER-REHMENE BIL-GAJBI FEBESHSHIRHU BIMEGFIRETIN WE ‘EXHRIN KERIMIN
  36,12,‘INNA NEHNU NUHJIL-MEWTA WE NEKTUBU MA KADDEMU WE ‘ATHAREHUM WE KULLE SHEJ’IN ‘HSEJNAHU FI ‘IMAMIN MUBININ
  36,13,WE EDRIB LEHUM METHELÆN ‘ESHABEL-KARJETI ‘IDH XHA’EHAL-MURSELUNE
  36,14,‘IDH ‘ERSELNA ‘ILEJHIMU ETHNEJNI FEKEDHDHEBUHUMA FE’AZZEZNA BITHALITHIN FEKALU ‘INNA ‘ILEJKUM MURSELUNE
  36,15,KALU MA ‘ENTUM ‘ILLA BESHERUN MITHLUNA WE MA ‘ENZELE ER-REHMANU MIN SHEJ’IN ‘IN ‘ENTUM ‘ILLA TEKDHIBUNE
  36,16,KALU REBBUNA JA’LEMU ‘INNA ‘ILEJKUM LEMURSELUNE
  36,17,WE MA ‘ALEJNA ‘ILLAL-BELAGUL-MUBINU
  36,18,KALU ‘INNA TETEJJERNA BIKUM LE’IN LEM TENTEHU LENERXHUMENNEKUM WE LEJEMESSENNEKUM MINNA ‘ADHABUN ‘ELIMUN
  36,19,KALU TA’IRUKUM ME’AKUM ‘E’IN DHUKKIRTUM BEL ‘ENTUM KAWMUN MUSRIFUNE
  36,20,WE XHA’E MIN ‘EKSAL-MEDINETI REXHULUN JES’A KALE JA KAWMI ETTEBI’UL-MURSELINE
  36,21,ETTEBI’U MEN LA JES’ELUKUM ‘EXHRÆN WE HUM MUHTEDUNE
  36,22,WE MA LIJE LA ‘A’BUDUL-LEDHI FETERENI WE ‘ILEJHI TURXHA’UNE
  36,23,‘E’ETTEHIDHU MIN DUNIHI ‘ALIHETEN ‘IN JURIDNI ER-REHMANU BIDURRIN LA TUGNI ‘ANNI SHEFA’ATUHUM SHEJ’ÆN WE LA JUNKIDHUNI
  36,24,‘INNI ‘IDHÆN LEFI DELALIN MUBININ
  36,25,‘INNI ‘AMENTU BIREBBIKUM FASMA’UNI
  36,26,KILE EDHULIL-XHENNETE KALE JA LEJTE KAWMI JA’LEMUNE
  36,27,BIMA GAFERE LI RABBI WE XHE’ALENI MINEL-MUKREMINE